Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 17th February 2025

Your Privacy Matters to Us

Welcome to Balloon Hunt. We understand the importance of privacy and are committed to ensuring that your personal information remains completely secure. 
This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and protection of your data.

1. No Data Collection

At Puzzled Raccoon Apps, we value your privacy. Our app is designed to function without collecting, storing, or processing any personal information from users. 
We do not collect any data that could identify you personally, including but not limited to:

- Personal Identifiable Information (PII): Such as your name, address, phone number, email, or any other information that can identify you.
- Financial Information: Any payment details, banking information, or credit card details.
- Usage Data: No information about your interactions with the app, including login times, duration of use, or specific features accessed.
- Location Data: We do not track or store your geographical location.
- Device Information: We do not collect any data about your device, such as model, operating system, or IP address.

2. No Third-Party Services

Our app does not integrate with any third-party services or platforms that might collect or process your data. This means:

- No third-party analytics services.
- No social media integrations.
- No third-party advertising networks.
- No external payment gateways.

3. Offline Usage

Balloon Hunt is designed to function fully offline, ensuring that your data remains with you and is not transmitted over the internet.

4. Children's Privacy

Since Balloon Hunt does not collect any data, it is fully compliant with children's privacy laws. 
We do not knowingly collect, store, or use any personal information from children under the age of 13, or any other age as required by law.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

While our commitment to protecting your privacy will never change, this Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to reflect changes 
in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We encourage you to periodically review this policy for the latest information on our privacy practices.

6. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, or if you believe there has been a violation of this policy, 
please contact us at puzzledraccoonapps@gmail.com.

Balloon Hunt
Puzzled Raccoon Apps
puzzledraccoonapps@gmail.com  

---

This Privacy Policy is designed to assure you that your privacy is protected when using Balloon Hunt. Since we do not collect or store any of your data, 
you can use our app with complete peace of mind.
